ZH: 此生我只愿与你共度余生。
EN: In this lifetime, I only want to spend the rest of my days with you.

ZH: 此生无悔，因为有了你。
EN: I have no regrets in this lifetime because of you.

ZH: 你是我此生中最重要的人。
EN: You are the most important person in my life.

ZH: 此生最大的遗憾就是错过了和你在一起的时光。
EN: The biggest regret in this lifetime is missing out on the time spent with you.

ZH: 此生唯一的心愿是能和你白头到老。
EN: The only wish in this lifetime is to grow old with you.

ZH: 此生我愿意为你付出一切。
EN: In this lifetime, I am willing to give everything for you.

ZH: 此生有你，便是我的幸福。
EN: Having you in this lifetime is my happiness.

ZH: 此生只要与你在一起，其他都不重要。
EN: As long as I am with you in this lifetime, nothing else matters.

ZH: 此生无论发生什么，我都会陪伴在你身旁。
EN: No matter what happens in this lifetime, I will always be by your side.

ZH: 我希望我们的爱能延续到此生的尽头。
EN: I hope our love will last until the end of this lifetime.

ZH: 愿此生与你一同闻到花香、看到风景。
EN: May this lifetime be filled with the fragrance of flowers and beautiful sights with you.

ZH: 此生我愿与你相守，直至永远。
EN: In this lifetime, I am willing to stay with you until eternity.

ZH: 此生的每一天都因为你而充满了爱和快乐。
EN: Every day of this lifetime is filled with love and happiness because of you.

ZH: 我感恩此生中遇到你这个人。
EN: I am grateful to have met you in this lifetime.

ZH: 在我此生的记忆中，你是永恒的存在。
EN: In the memories of my life, you are the eternal presence.

ZH: 此生的最大幸运就是拥有你的爱。
EN: The greatest fortune of this lifetime is having your love.

ZH: 你给了我此生最美好的回忆。
EN: You have given me the most beautiful memories of this lifetime.

ZH: 此生无论有多漫长，我都愿意等待你的归来。
EN: No matter how long this lifetime may be, I am willing to wait for your return.

ZH: 我愿意与你一起经历此生的风风雨雨。
EN: I am willing to go through the ups and downs of this lifetime with you.

ZH: 无论此生是否有来生，我都会永远爱你。
EN: Whether there is an afterlife in this lifetime or not, I will love you forever.
